import Style from '../../pages/register/style.css';


export default function Register() {

  

    return (
        <form>
          <label>
            Nome:
            <input type="text" name="name"/>
          </label>
          <label>
            Senha:
            <input type="password" name="senha"/>
          </label>
          <label>
            Cpf:
            <input type="text" name="cpf"/>
          </label>
          <label>
            Crm:
            <input type="text" name="crm"/>
          </label>
          <label>
            Especialização:
            <input type="text" name="specialization"/>
          </label>
          <label>
            Telefone1:
            <input type="text" name="phoneOne"/>
          </label><label>
            Telefone2:
            <input type="text" name="phoneTwo"/>
          </label>
          
          <button>Cadastrar</button>
        </form>
      
    );
  }
